{"tid":1592853,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"越來越覺得自己配唔上男朋友","createTime":"2019-09-24T20:42:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-27T05:53:11.000Z","uid":142854,"like":4,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"525eb32997eb1da28b38becceb2d04dc30de31d8","tid":1592853,"uid":142854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T20:42:30.000Z","msg":"男朋友係同我一齊既第一日就承諾會好好照顧我<br />\n事實上佢係一個好有責任感既人 由我同佢一齊住既日子開始<br />\n<br />\n每胡定時叫我起床 定時接我放工<br />\n屋入面既家務同埋瑣碎野大部分都做哂 我講過想睇既戲佢咩都唔理隔一兩日就去同我睇<br />\n有幾次我病左佢專登請個幾個半日假去睇我...<br />\n<br />\n佢係佢朋友入面個圈子叫做受歡迎 而且又靚仔<br />\n有時候我都唔知佢點解會揀自己<br />\n平日又懶 淨係識返工 食 訓 份人又唔識講野 朋友唔多<br />\n成個人生就好似寄生緊佢咁(雖然我好愛佢)<br />\n去到今朝沖涼既時候發現自己既袋底泥冇哂 果刻我真係喊左先黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n到底有冇人明啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76b5a426307db916a61147365801d1bfb31d2d55","tid":1592853,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T20:42:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/biFbOWs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbiFbOWs.png&h=404dfcfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【929行動】大家好，我地係Chinazi。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1590320\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1590320</a>"},{"pid":"e48282b7b8e82c40087eea8a4367f791ad6687db","tid":1592853,"uid":271289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T20: